Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:10.93,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 你拿到了吗 - 是他帮我越狱的\N{\rEng}Did you get it? He helped me escape prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:13.45,Chn,,0,0,0,,我问你有没有拿到终极魔方\N{\rEng}Did you get the Ultimate Cube?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:14.76,Chn,,0,0,0,,行吧 是紫色的\N{\rEng}Oh, it's purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:16.21,Chn,,0,0,0,,你说过它是紫色的\N{\rEng}Y-You said it was purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:17.59,Chn,,0,0,0,,我是说我的那个是紫的\N{\rEng}I said mine was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:19.25,Chn,,0,0,0,,我不知道都是紫的\N{\rEng}I didn't know they all were.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:21.42,Chn,,0,0,0,,现在知道了 感谢Chichi\N{\rEng}And now we do, thanks to Chichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:22.80,Chn,,0,0,0,,是Chachi\N{\rEng}Chachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:26.43,Chn,,0,0,0,,所以 呃 什什什么时候能给我\N{\rEng}So, uh, w-w-when do I get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:27.88,Chn,,0,0,0,,给你啥 一个拥抱吗\N{\rEng}Get what, a hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:29.60,Chn,,0,0,0,,等我们找到有园艺橡胶管的星球再说吧\N{\rEng}Let's find a planet with a garden hose first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:30.78,Chn,,0,0,0,,要龙啊 龙啊\N{\rEng}A dragon. A dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:33.03,Chn,,0,0,0,,是你让我翘课去帮你打机器人的\N{\rEng}You asked me to cut class and fight robots with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:34.34,Chn,,0,0,0,,我说 “不”\N{\rEng}I said, "No."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:35.58,Chn,,0,0,0,,你说 “几百万条生命就在此一战了”\N{\rEng}You said, "Millions of lives depend on it."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.62,0:00:37.24,Chn,,0,0,0,,我说 “给我龙我就干”\N{\rEng}I said, "I'll do it for a dragon."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:38.93,Chn,,0,0,0,,你说 “啥都行”\N{\rEng}You said, "Whatever."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:40.28,Chn,,0,0,0,,我要我的龙\N{\rEng}I want my dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:41.89,Chn,,0,0,0,,Morty 你知道什么人才喜欢龙吗\N{\rEng}You know who's into dragons, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:43.99,Chn,,0,0,0,,拒绝承认自己信基督的书呆子们\N{\rEng}Nerds that refuse to admit they're Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:45.90,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 我要龙 - 给你双火箭鞋怎么样\N{\rEng}I want my dragon. Let me give you rocket shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:47.38,Chn,,0,0,0,,金刚狼的爪子呢\N{\rEng}Let me give you Wolverine claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.41,0:00:49.00,Chn,,0,0,0,,要不来一顶他妈的火箭帽吧\N{\rEng}Let me give you a fucking rocket hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:50.56,Chn,,0,0,0,,记得和火箭鞋配套使用\N{\rEng}Just be sure to use it with the rocket shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:51.83,Chn,,0,0,0,,不然你的头会被甩掉\N{\rEng}or it'll rip your head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:53.90,Chn,,0,0,0,,我要我的龙 我要我的龙\N{\rEng}I want my dragon! I want my dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:55.25,Chn,,0,0,0,,我要我的龙\N{\rEng}I want my dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:00:58.25,Chn,,0,0,0,,哦 操\N{\rEng}Oh, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.29,0:01:00.01,Chn,,0,0,0,,完犊子了\N{\rEng}Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:04.33,Chn,,0,0,0,,爸 你还好吗\N{\rEng}Dad, are you okay?
