Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:07.78,Chn,,0,0,0,,我没事儿\N{\rEng}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.81,0:01:10.40,Chn,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地\N{\rEng}Oh, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:12.30,Chn,,0,0,0,,爸 你是不答应Morty要给他条龙\N{\rEng}Dad, did you promise Morty a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:13.85,Chn,,0,0,0,,次奥奥奥\N{\rEng}Fuuuuuuu--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.72,0:01:48.93,Chn,,0,0,0,,把血滴在这儿 还有这儿\N{\rEng}Bleed here and here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.11,Chn,,0,0,0,,我才不掺和\N{\rEng}I'm not co-bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:51.69,Chn,,0,0,0,,基于以下条约所述之协定\N{\rEng}Under authority of our treaty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:53.80,Chn,,0,0,0,,“在人类世界与龙的王国之间”\N{\rEng}'twixt the realms of dragon and man...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:55.18,Chn,,0,0,0,,哦天 我还是头一回参加同志婚礼\N{\rEng}Oh, my God, it's my first gay wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:56.53,Chn,,0,0,0,,Summer\N{\rEng}Summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:58.70,Chn,,0,0,0,,在此 我将这条高贵的龙与他的驾驭者\N{\rEng}...I hereby bind this noble serpent and rider
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.73,0:02:00.36,Chn,,0,0,0,,进行灵魂绑定\N{\rEng}at the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:03.36,Chn,,0,0,0,,这本书上写了和龙有关的咒语以及其他知识\N{\rEng}Here's your tome of dragon spells and lore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:04.71,Chn,,0,0,0,,上面有你需要的一切\N{\rEng}That'll have everything you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:05.98,Chn,,0,0,0,,和你的龙好好玩儿吧\N{\rEng}Enjoy your dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:07.61,Chn,,0,0,0,,听着 龙 这个房子里有如下规则\N{\rEng}Okay, dragon, here's the house rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:10.54,Chn,,0,0,0,,吾名茅彻\N{\rEng}My name is Balthromaw,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:13.30,Chn,,0,0,0,,天之破坏者 山之戮徒\N{\rEng}breaker of sky, slayer of mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:15.96,Chn,,0,0,0,,第一条 自己铲屎\N{\rEng}Rule one -- You are now scooper of your own poops,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:19.17,Chn,,0,0,0,,不然我会像拆掉黑光海报一样对待你\N{\rEng}or I will take you down like the black-light poster you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:20.96,Chn,,0,0,0,,其他没了 就这一条\N{\rEng}I don't got any more rules. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:24.17,Chn,,0,0,0,,你应该不想在照片里被圈出来吧\N{\rEng}I'm guessing you'd rather not be tagged in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:26.34,Chn,,0,0,0,,好吧 我上钩了\N{\rEng}Okay, I'll bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:27.65,Chn,,0,0,0,,那只会说话的猫是什么情况\N{\rEng}What's with the talking cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:29.27,Chn,,0,0,0,,是龙 你个二货\N{\rEng}It's a dragon, dip knob.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.76,Chn,,0,0,0,,我知道屋外的是龙\N{\rEng}I know that's a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.59,Chn,,0,0,0,,我说的是我房间里的说话猫\N{\rEng}I'm talking about the talking cat in my bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:37.35,Chn,,0,0,0,,Jerry 为什么我在给Morty一条会说话的龙的同时 又给你一只会说话的猫呢\N{\rEng}Jerry, why would I give Morty a talking dragon and you a talking cat at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:38.84,Chn,,0,0,0,,那岂不是撞车了\N{\rEng}Those concepts bump.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.60,Chn,,0,0,0,,如果你和猫对话了 这事儿确实不正常\N{\rEng}If you're talking to a cat, it's an abnormal event
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:43.05,Chn,,0,0,0,,但与我无关 就像你去冥王星\N{\rEng}unrelated to me like when you went to Pluto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:44.60,Chn,,0,0,0,,或者干我女儿\N{\rEng}or fucked my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:47.33,Chn,,0,0,0,,好吧 也没必要这么乱咬人\N{\rEng}Okay, there's really no need to get savage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:49.95,Chn,,0,0,0,,所以呢\N{\rEng}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:51.68,Chn,,0,0,0,,他说你能说话跟他没啥关系\N{\rEng}Eh, he says he has nothing to do with your talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:53.95,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 跟你说过喽 - 所以你为什么会说话呢\N{\rEng}Told you. So then why are you talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:56.44,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 这有什么要紧的呢 - 难道不要紧吗\N{\rEng}Why should that matter? Why should it not matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:03:00.55,Chn,,0,0,0,,我怎么能分清是不是我出幻觉了 Rick说这事儿不正常\N{\rEng}How do I know I'm not hallucinating? Rick said this is an abnormal event.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.58,Chn,,0,0,0,,你总是需要Rick来告诉你发生什么了吗\N{\rEng}Do you always need Rick to tell you what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.69,Chn,,0,0,0,,也许你该停止发问了\N{\rEng}Maybe it's time you stopped asking questions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:07.04,Chn,,0,0,0,,然后开始去找点儿乐子\N{\rEng}and started having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:11.19,Chn,,0,0,0,,哇哦 行吧\N{\rEng}Wow, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:14.34,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 那 你想要什么呢 - 我想要你带我去机场\N{\rEng}So, what do you want? I want you to take us to the airport
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.90,Chn,,0,0,0,,然后买两张去佛罗里达的头等舱机票\N{\rEng}and get us two first-class tickets to Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:20.35,Chn,,0,0,0,,为什 我 我可以的\N{\rEng}Why, I -- I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:27.56,Chn,,0,0,0,,这也太酷了吧\N{\rEng}Oh, this is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:34.02,Chn,,0,0,0,,恭候您的下个命令\N{\rEng}I await your next command.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:36.37,Chn,,0,0,0,,别别别 没有谁命令谁\N{\rEng}Whoa, whoa, whoa. Nobody is commanding anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:41.27,Chn,,0,0,0,,我更喜欢你我平等相处 共同翱翔天际 那 那你现在想做什么呢\N{\rEng}I love soaring through the sky with you as equals. W-What do you want to do?
