Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:47.38,Chn,,0,0,0,,一觉睡到人类灭绝\N{\rEng}until the Age of Man expires.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.45,Chn,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:50.03,Chn,,0,0,0,,要不咱们取个折中\N{\rEng}Split the diff?
