Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.42,Chn,,0,0,0,,悉听尊便\N{\rEng}As you command.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.08,Chn,,0,0,0,,好嘞 一会儿见\N{\rEng}Okay, see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:03:59.42,Chn,,0,0,0,,这 这还是挺有意思的\N{\rEng}T-This is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.77,Chn,,0,0,0,,对 可不是嘛\N{\rEng}Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:04.05,Chn,,0,0,0,,这是啥剧来着 《识股寻凶》么\N{\rEng}What's this show called, "Ass"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:06.74,Chn,,0,0,0,,对 和《识骨寻踪》差不多 区别在于这剧破的是屁股谜案\N{\rEng}Yeah, it's like "Bones," but they solve ass crimes.
